room_title: Escape room "The Trophy Room" by 13th Hour Haunted House in New York
room_description: John Hayden has been collecting trophies of his victims over the years, although he loves his trophies he is still on the search for the ultimate trophy, the one that always gets away. You have 60 minutes to find the trophy he has been searching for and survive the room. do you have what it takes?
